        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Even in the third year of Asa did Baasha slay him — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "It was threatened, (",
        "children": []
